n=u.Q+o+'" tarz\u0131n\u0131 se\xe7ti (anket kart\u0131ndan).\n\n\u015eU KARTLARI \xdcRET:\n1. "style_analysis" \u2014 Bu stilin detaylar\u0131: style_name, confidence: 1.0, description, color_palette (4 renk), mood, tags\n2. "product_grid" \u2014 Bu stile uygun 3 \xfcr\xfcn (isim + fiyat + neden). title: "'+o+' stiline \xf6zel \xfcr\xfcnler"\n3. "question_chips" \u2014 "Bu stili uygulamak ister misin?" se\xe7enekleri: ["Evet, salon i\xe7in", "Evet, yatak odas\u0131 i\xe7in", "\xd6nce foto\u011fraf \xe7ekeyim \ud83d\udcf8", "Ba\u015fka stiller de g\xf6ster"]\n\nmessage: "'+o+' harika bir tercih! \ud83c\udfaf"\n\nSADECE JSON.\n'
